# Technology Stack

## Core Technologies
- React 18
- TypeScript
- Vite
- Electron (for desktop app)
- Tailwind CSS
- Zustand (state management)
- React Router DOM

## UI Components
- Radix UI (base components)
- Lucide React (icons)
- Shadcn UI (component library)
- Lexical (rich text editor)
- Monaco Editor (code editor)

## Data Management
- SQLite (via better-sqlite3)
- SWR (data fetching)
- React Hook Form (form handling)
- Zod (schema validation)

## AI Integration
- OpenAI
- Anthropic
- Google AI
- Mistral AI
- And other AI providers via @ai-sdk packages

## Development Tools
- ESLint
- Prettier
- Vitest (testing)
- TypeScript
- PNPM (package manager)

